rint. It also adds a secret \"Specialist Only\" Hornet car with a code, which allows players to customize the original Daytona USA Hornet to their specifications.\n\nThe game saw no home ports, only appearing in \"Like a Dragon Gaiden: The Man Who Erased His Name\" as \"Sega Racing Classic 2\".","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/daytona-usa-2-power-edition","websites":[{"id":815242,"url":"https://segaretro.org/Daytona_USA_2:_Power_Edition","type":{"id":2,"type":"Community Wiki"}}]}